# Summary

| Requirement | Solution |
|-------------|----------|
|Number rows|ROW_NUMBER()|
|Competition ranking|RANK()|
|Dense ranking|DENSE_RANK()|
|Previous record|LAG()|
|Next record|LEAD()|
|Restart calculation|PARTITION BY|
|Define sequence|ORDER BY|
